MTProxy upstream licence
========================

The server/ directory is a `git subtree` of the active upstream
github.com/teleproxy/teleproxy (community-maintained continuation of
the archived github.com/TelegramMessenger/MTProxy). The upstream
licence applies UNCHANGED to every file under this directory,
including fork-local additions (net-type3-dispatch.{c,h},
net-type3-stats.{c,h}, etc.).

The upstream licence text lives at:
  https://github.com/teleproxy/teleproxy/blob/master/LICENSE
(ancestor, for reference:
  https://github.com/TelegramMessenger/MTProxy/blob/master/LICENSE )

TODO(server-v0.1.0): vendor the upstream LICENSE text verbatim here
during the first subtree pull. Recording server/UPSTREAM.md with the
SHA.

We cannot and do not relicense this directory. If you are building on
Type3 with a permissive licence in mind, consume `spec/` + `lib/` +
`conformance/` — all Apache 2.0 — and implement a fresh server.
